snippet.title: OVERWHELM Release Trailer - E3 2018
snippet.description:
A game by Ruari O'Sullivan

http://overwhelmgame.com

This is an action horror world where enemies get power-ups and you don’t. You're outnumbered, low on ammunition and the paranoia sets in. 

http://overwhelmgame.com

CREDITS
Additional Art by Sven Ruther
Key Art by Guillaume Singelin
Trailer by Keith Shelter
